      "content": "i spent fifteen years on the simulation data. fifteen years. and it was all wrong. just a fundamental error in the math that i missed. everything i published, every lecture, every grant... it's all just noise now. i feel like a ghost in my own life. there isn't even a person left here, just a mistake that won't stop moving.",
